data.description: Located in the highly desirable neighborhood of San Luis Rey Estates, this Mid-Century Modern, visually rich home boasts a stunning setting against the picturesque backdrop of Oceanside Hills. Designed by renowned architect, A. Quincy Jones, this home is characterized and defined by its designer elegance, flair, and eclectic charm. Known as the Lido floor-plan, this home epitomizes the essence of Southern California living, presenting like a feature in a high-end magazine spread. Step into the opulent, one-of-a-kind courtyard/breezeway, embellished with designer finishes and lush greenery leading to the front door. The interior features high-vaulted and beamed ceilings, open concept living, a reconfigured layout that maximizes space, all featuring top-of-the-line designer finishes and materials.  Experience unparalleled luxury with the new, flawlessly-designed backyard, created for both dreamers and entertainers. Every detail has been carefully and meticulously considered, from the outdoor lounge living room, where marble flooring, designer finishes, and Sonos surround sound speakers create the perfect ambiance, to the relaxing Modfire fire pit, surrounded by cozy fireside seating. Unwind and immerse yourself in the beauty of nature with the outdoor bath/shower combo. The pool, heated by solar energy, boasts Bluetooth-controlled custom lighting and self-cleaning technology.Ranging from 3 to 6 feet deep and 15x30 feet in size, it is equipped with a convenient baja shelf, acting as the perfect middle ground between the pool and the poolside. As the cherry on top, you can enjoy a private viewing of skydivers from the backyard. A lavish 200-square-foot guest casita and outdoor bathroom have been added. The side yard is outfitted with premium artificial grass. Enjoy a leisurely bike ride to the beach and nearby trails. Positioned approximately 4 miles from Downtown Oceanside, Oceanside Pier, Oceanside Beach, the San Luis Rey River Hiking and Biking Trails, and Oceanside Harbor, this property offers a perfect blend of serene surroundings and an exciting outdoor lifestyle. Situated near multiple grocery stores, dining options, bars, entertainment, and quick and convenient freeway access. Fully equipped in-home gym. Energy efficient and cost savings with FULLY OWNED, paid-off solar panels.
